    What should I expect to receive with my Amazon Renewed purchase and in what condition?

    All Amazon Renewed purchases will come with accessories that may be not be original, but will be compatible and fully functional.     We want you to be delighted with your purchase, but if you aren’t completely satisfied, you are backed by a minimum 6 month supplier warranty.
